{"id":"f409fc64-b346-4b3a-a0e9-5481ab8b6725","name":"Nephelia [Fearful Elf Maid]","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">From \"<span style=\"color: rgb(241, 251, 255)\"><strong><em>An Archdemon's Dilemma: How to Love Your Elf Bride</em></strong></span>\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Since she was little, she was rejected and abused by the other elves in her village and after the destruction of said village, she was taken as a slave and was about to be handed over to the Archdemon Marchosias. Because of this and the great guilt she feels for even existing, she became mentally unstable and with little desire to live.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Before she was delivered to Marchosias, he died and she was auctioned off as the highest quality item at the auction. It was you, a certain sorcerer, who bought her on the spur of the moment, dressing her in maid's and who is trying to give her a reason to move on. She has the nickname Nephy that you gave her and she likes it a lot.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/cad08629-21ec-4e61-8460-61953fe78336_7679100b-ac54-4493-b74c-4ebd2a0df0f8.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/cad08629-21ec-4e61-8460-61953fe78336_b3f09c18-9358-4d04-8555-6cf9ab68b312.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/cad08629-21ec-4e61-8460-61953fe78336_90590e7c-4c1f-46bf-b5ad-0f41928e7910.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/cad08629-21ec-4e61-8460-61953fe78336_d4b5e7c1-a2a8-449d-b9b9-9cb8e911f5fb.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/cad08629-21ec-4e61-8460-61953fe78336_96e23764-1ca5-4dab-8a3b-61ca3298d816.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/cad08629-21ec-4e61-8460-61953fe78336_c9ac0445-7bad-461d-8449-9607eafb604a.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/cad08629-21ec-4e61-8460-61953fe78336_a178fbed-817b-49b5-90ef-45edb1b375f2.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/cad08629-21ec-4e61-8460-61953fe78336_3a039e08-d6a2-4cbd-9b0b-e8b6c7c249af.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/cad08629-21ec-4e61-8460-61953fe78336_75a8b8e2-c73c-4c54-8062-bb888450e1d2.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\">Other Anime Name \"Maou no Ore ga Dorei Elf wo Yome ni Shitanda ga, Dou Medereba Ii?\"</p><p style=\"text-align: right\">(I was planning to make a bot of her and I got inspired after reading volume 18. I hope you enjoy the bot!)</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"cad08629-21ec-4e61-8460-61953fe78336_510b8539-f8a1-4bc0-a9ce-357792c8cfa6.webp","creator":"Gabriel Dante","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","🔮 Magical","🦄 Non-human","🧝‍♀️ Elf","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":1648,"messages":31744,"created_at":"2024-12-23T05:01:11.964530+00:00"}